px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">Abel (@theweeknd) 分享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p>到目前为止，这位音乐家已经通过他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-weeknd-and-playboi-carti-team-up-on-new-single-timeless-3797591">之前与 Playboi Carti 合作的《Timeless》（</a>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Pharrell">Pharrell</a>联合制作）和另一首新单曲《Dancing In The Flames》（于 9 月推出）的形式分享了这张专辑的品味。 。他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-shares-snippet-of-new-music-in-cinematic-teaser-3777326">最近还预览了多首未发行的歌曲</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-the-weeknd-played-at-his-special-sao-paulo-concert-3791657">“Wake Me Up”、“Take Me Back To LA”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-previews-dancey-new-song-open-hearts-at-sydney-concert-3805355">“Open Hearts”</a> 。</p><p>这张专辑将于 5 月推出，并附有一部同名长片，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-announces-release-date-for-hurry-up-tomorrow-film-3824134">The Weeknd、Jenna Ortega 和 Barry Keoghan 主演</a>。它被描述为专辑的“延伸”。</p><p> 《周末报》最近还讨论了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-on-why-he-wants-to-retire-the-moniker-ive-overcome-every-challenge-as-this-persona-3828072">他计划废除目前绰号的原因</a>。他确认放弃 Weeknd 的绰号并不意味着他要退休，他说：“一切都需要感觉像是一个挑战。现在对我来说，周末，无论那是什么，它已经被掌握了。没有人能比我把周末做得更好，我也不会比现在做得更好。我认为我已经克服了作为这个角色的每一个挑战，这就是为什么我对这部电影感到非常兴奋，因为我喜欢这个挑战。”</p><p>在其他与洛杉矶山火相关的新闻中，人们还做出了无数的慈善努力来帮助受山火影响的人们，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a>的基金会<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-foundation-announces-2-5million-donation-to-la-wildfire-relief-3828303">捐赠250万美元用于救灾工作</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-launches-fund-for-families-displaced-by-the-la-wildfires-3828081">帕丽斯·希尔顿捐赠10万美元并启动一项基金来帮助流离失所的家庭</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jamie-lee-curtis-donates-1million-to-los-angeles-wildfire-relief-efforts-3828267">在与加州州长加文·纽瑟姆 (Gavin Newsom) 会谈后，杰米·李·柯蒂斯 (Jamie Lee Curtis) 捐赠了 100 万美元用于救灾工作，</a>而查莉<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">·XCX (Charli XCX)</a>敦促向<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-urges-brands-gifting-her-clothing-to-instead-donate-it-to-those-affected-by-horrific-la-wildfires-3828185">她寄送衣服的品牌将其捐赠给受洛杉矶持续山火影响的人们</a>。</p><p>昨天，据报道吉他中心<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guitar-center-offers-to-replace-instruments-lost-in-los-angeles-wildfires-3828262">宣布了一项新计划，该计划将帮助受影响的音乐家</a>更换乐器或装备。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-delays-new-album-hurry-up-tomorrow-due-to-los-angeles-wildfires-3828567">《The Weeknd》因洛杉矶野火推迟新专辑《Hurry Up Tomorrow》的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
广受好评的音乐博士“Dig!”重返电影院庆祝上映20周年https://www.nme.com/news/film/acclaimed-music-doc-dig-returning-to-cinemas-20th-anniversary-3828546?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=acclaimed-music-doc-dig-returning-到电影院 20 周年纪念日Sophie ButcherTue, 14 Jan 2025 00:01:38 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3828546 <p><img width="1920" height="1080" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="&#39;挖！ XX&#39;。图片来源：Dogwoof" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1.jpg 1920w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1-400x225.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1-800x450.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1-696x392.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1-1392x783.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1-1068x601.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p><p>新修复版将在大银幕上仅放映一晚</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/acclaimed-music-doc-dig-returning-to-cinemas-20th-anniversary-3828546">广受好评的音乐博士“Dig！” 《重返影院 20 周年》</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相。</p> ; <p><img width="1920" height="1080" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="&#39;挖！ XX&#39;。图片来源：Dogwoof" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1.jpg 1920w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1-400x225.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1-800x450.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1-696x392.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1-1392x783.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-1-1068x601.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p><p>广受好评的音乐纪录片<i>DIG!</i>重返电影院庆祝上映 20 周年。</p><p><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/best-music-documentaries-to-see-before-you-die-3055958"><b>史上 50 部最佳音乐纪录片</b></a></p><p><i>DIG!</i>荣获 2004 年圣丹斯电影节评委会大奖。由翁迪·蒂莫纳 (Ondi Timoner) 执导，描绘了两个美国摇滚乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-dandy-warhols">丹迪·沃霍尔 (The Dandy Warhols)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-jonestown-massacre">布莱恩·琼斯镇大屠杀 (The Brian Jonestown Massacre)</a>的不同旅程。这部影片历时七年拍摄，跟踪乐队的巡演并记录了他们之间的创作紧张关系。</p><p>这部电影经过扩展、增强和重新构思，打造出一个新版本<i>——DIG！ XX</i> – 今年春天将重新发布。最初由 Dandy Warhols 的 Courtney Taylor 担任旁白，新版本则由 Brian Jonestown Massacre 的 Joel Gion 担任新旁白。 </p><figure id="attachment_3828553" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828553" style="width: 1920px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828553" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-2.jpg" alt="&#39;挖！ XX&#39;。图片来源：Dogwoof" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-2.jpg 1920w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-2-400x225.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-2-800x450.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-2-696x392.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-2-1392x783.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-2-1068x601.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828553" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;挖！ XX&#39;。图片来源：Dogwoof</figcaption></figure><p><i>挖！ 《XX》</i>将于 3 月 25 日在英国电影院仅放映一晚，并于 3 月 28 日起限量上映。</p><p>官方简介如下：“原始纪录片捕捉了独立音乐史上的决定性时刻，并在世界各地获得奖项，同时因其真实性和大胆而受到赞扬。<i>挖！ XX</i>将史诗般的故事带到了现在，深入探讨了艺术与名誉之间的冲突，两个独立乐队在主流的吸引力和成功的代价之间进行了角力。</p><p> “从高风险的野心到路上生活的严峻现实，这部纪录片以未经过滤的方式揭示了摇滚乐的内心挣扎，同时重点关注了 1990 年代两个最具影响力的独立乐队所面临的挑战。” </p><figure id="attachment_3828554" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828554" style="width: 1920px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828554" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-3.jpg" alt="&#39;挖！ XX&#39;。图片来源：Dogwoof" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-3.jpg 1920w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-3-400x225.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-3-800x450.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-3-696x392.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-3-1392x783.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dig-xx-doc-3-1068x601.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828554" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;挖！ XX&#39;。图片来源：Dogwoof</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/the-dandy-warhols-dig-was-a-huge-turning-point-it-was-brutal-for-us-3578366">2024 年，The Dandy Warhols 的泰勒在接受<i>NME</i>采访</a>时表示：“希望<i>DIG 成立 20 周年！</i>这将有助于提高我们的新唱片“Rockmaker”的知名度，但至于电影，我不在乎。</p><p> “这不准确。这最终成为了一件非常卑鄙和令人讨厌的事情。我们只是作为布莱恩·琼斯镇大屠杀的陪衬。这是一个可怕的情况。除了[布莱恩·琼斯镇大屠杀成员]乔尔·吉恩的精彩时刻很有趣之外，这只是直接的消极情绪。”</p><p>当被问及他是否后悔拍摄这部电影时，泰勒说：“是的，当然。那时人们还不习惯被拍摄。我们被告知她（导演翁迪·蒂莫德）正在以同样的方式操纵琼斯镇。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="挖！ XX - 英国官方预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ye6DtQ7j4FI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “她会钻进他们的货车里说：‘嘿，丹迪夫妇现在正在录音室里和大卫·鲍伊一起工作。你身上发生过类似的事情吗？’，他们就会很<i>生气</i>，并努力让她得到镜头。”</p><p>他继续说道：“这与音乐无关；她只是想激怒我们。中午睡了两个小时后，她会叫醒我说：“国会唱片公司总裁正在打电话。”你必须和他谈谈！”，因为我快要吐了，而且我的头很痛。</p><p> “但这一切都构成了一款有趣的手表——我只是希望里面不是我的乐队。这是一个巨大的转折点。这对我们来说是残酷的。但这成就了安东的职业生涯。没有它，他就不会拥有自己的职业生涯。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/acclaimed-music-doc-dig-returning-to-cinemas-20th-anniversary-3828546">广受好评的音乐博士“Dig！” 《重返影院 20 周年》</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相。</p> ;
凯莉·安德伍德将在唐纳德·特朗普的就职典礼上表演https://www.nme.com/news/music/carrie-underwood-is-billed-to-perform-at-donald-trumps-inauguration-3828551?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=carrie-underwood-is-billed-在唐纳德·特朗普就职典礼上表演Aneesa AhmedMon, 13 Jan 2025 22:51:25 +0000 Music NewsNewsPoliticsCountryDiscoDonald Trump https://www.nme.com/?p=3828551 <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯莉·安德伍德。图片来源：Craig T Fruchtman" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Village People主唱维克多·威利斯(Victor Willis)也表示，乐队将“参加就职活动”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/carrie-underwood-is-billed-to-perform-at-donald-trumps-inauguration-3828551">凯莉·安德伍德 (Carrie Underwood) 预计在唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 就职典礼上表演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯莉·安德伍德。图片来源：Craig T Fruchtman" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Carrie-Underwood.-Credit-Craig-T-Fruchtman-min-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/carrie-underwood">凯莉·安德伍德</a>预计将在本月晚些时候的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>第二次就职典礼上表演。</p><p>特朗普将于 2025 年 1 月 20 日在华盛顿特区宣誓就任总统，格莱美奖得主嘉莉·安德伍德 (Carrie Underwood) 将作为音乐嘉宾登上舞台。一位发言人向<a href="https://www.axios.com/2025/01/13/carrie-underwood-trump-inauguration" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Axios</em></a>证实，她将参加表演“美丽的美国”的阵容。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://apnews.com/article/trump-inauguration-carrie-underwood-christopher-macchio-greenwood-601d590dd45b7f9544d06843f7279784" target="_blank" rel="noopener">美联社</a></em>报道，安德伍德周一在一份声明中表示：“我热爱我们的国家，很荣幸能被邀请在就职典礼上唱歌，并成为这一历史性活动的一小部分。” “在我们所有人必须本着团结精神并展望未来的时候，我很荣幸能够响应这一号召。”</p><p>安德伍德在<em>《美国偶像》</em>中开启了她的职业生涯，并以《Inside Your Heaven》和《Jesus》等歌曲而闻名，此前她曾在 2017 年乡村音乐奖上与布拉德·佩斯利 (Brad Paisley) 一起<a href="https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/carrie-underwood-brad-paisley-tease-trump-hilarious-music-parody-060702457.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">模仿特朗普</a>。两人演唱了她的热门歌曲《Before He Cheats》的改编版本，歌词取笑了特朗普当时反复无常的推特习惯：“观看很有趣，是的，这是肯定的/直到小火箭人发动核战争”。</p><p>此外，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/village-people">乡村人民</a>乐队主唱维克多·威利斯也表示，乐队将“参加特朗普的就职活动”。</p><p> “我们知道这不会让你们中的一些人高兴，但我们相信音乐的表演应该不考虑政治，”该组织在 Facebook 上<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=1126133308879573&amp;set=a.241070740719172&amp;locale=en_GB" target="_blank" rel="noopener">发帖</a>写道。 “我们的歌曲《YMCA》是一首全球赞歌，希望能帮助整个国家在一场混乱而分裂的竞选活动中团结起来，而我们最喜欢的候选人却失败了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3828558" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828558" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828558" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Village-People.-Getty-Images-min.jpg" alt="村里人。盖蒂图片分钟" width="2000" height="1240" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Village-People.-Getty-Images-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Village-People.-Getty-Images-min-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Village-People.-Getty-Images-min-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Village-People.-Getty-Images-min-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Village-People.-Getty-Images-min-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Village-People.-Getty-Images-min-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828558" class="wp-caption-text">美国迪斯科乐队 Village People 第二阵容的成员包括 David Hodo、Alex Briley、Glenn Hughes、Ray Simpson、Randy Jones 和 Philip Rose。 （摄影：Ron Galella/Ron Galella Collection via Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>据<em>美联社报道</em>，预计出席就职典礼的其他表演者包括特朗普最喜欢的乡村歌手李·格林伍德和歌剧歌手克里斯托弗·马基奥。</p><p>特朗普 2017 年就职典礼上，火箭女郎、摩门教堂合唱团和<em>美国达人</em>歌手杰基·伊万乔 (Jackie Evancho) 进行了表演。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aretha-franklin">艾瑞莎·富兰克林 (Aretha Franklin)</a>在 2009 年奥巴马的首次就职典礼上献唱，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯 (Beyonce)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kelly-clarkson">凯莉·克拉克森 (Kelly Clarkson)</a>在他 2013 年的第二次就职典礼上献唱。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/carrie-underwood-is-billed-to-perform-at-donald-trumps-inauguration-3828551">凯莉·安德伍德 (Carrie Underwood) 预计在唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 就职典礼上表演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
